title: Pokemon Sun and Pokemon Moon HQ OST (Ordered)
description:
Pokemon Sun & Moon original soundtrack theme song music extended and cleanly looped to play for about 10 minutes. Playlist organized by appearance.

Pokémon Sun and Pokémon Moon developed by Game Freak and published by The Pokémon Company.
Get the game: http://www.pokemon-sunmoon.com/en-us/
